summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Robert R. Fox and Maudie E. Fox, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, and D. B. Keniston, of Plymouth, New Hampshire, to the City of Seattle, dated the 8th day of December 1908, to certain portions of Lots three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7) and eight (8) in Block Twelve (12) and Lots nine 99), ten (10), eleven (11) and twelve (12) Block eleven (11) McKenzie & Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle.
